---
By: Ramana Maharshi
Locus:
  Page: 468
  Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Thoughts
---
Thoughts are our enemy. When we are free of thoughts, we are naturally
blissful. The gap between thoughts is our true state, it is the real Self.
Get rid of thoughts, be empty of them, be in a state of perpetual
thoughtlessness.
